  <brief_title>Use of a Vibrotactile Sensory Prosthesis in Patients With Postural Imbalance and Spatial Disorientation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of a Vibrotactile Sensory Aid Developed by the US Navy to Combat Pilot Disorientation as a Prosthesis in Patients With Postural Imbalance and Spatial Disorientation</official_title>
